## Setup and Install
1. Node version 16 
2. Java (JDK) 
3. Android SDK installed with virtual device (Android) 
4. Set JAVA_HOME and ANDROID_HOME env. variables 
5. Install dependencies: ```npm install```

## Running tests
Run android tests locally:
``` npm run android-test``` 

Run ios tests locally:
```npm run ios-test```

## Running on BrowserStack
Add a ```.env``` file and set the BROWSERSTACK_USER and BROWSERSTACK_KEY variables to your account credentials on BrowserStack.

Run android tests remotely on BrowserStack:
```npm run android-bs-test```
